l ever sell this exclusive phone to the general public.\", \"from\": 16365, \"to\": 16802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16509, \"end\": 16512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3047884197374671e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 16566, \"end\": 16579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Galaxy Z Flip\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_Flip\"}, {\"begin\": 16606, \"end\": 16616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999989295247, \"rank\": 1.0704818935517578e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 16736, \"end\": 16743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0145804755603644e-13, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if you are not an Olympian, you can at least pre-order the standard Galaxy Z Flip 6.\", \"from\": 16803, \"to\": 16891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16825, \"end\": 16833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999381544, \"rank\": 5.993146914763798e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not offer free beverages and transpo